 * await session.connect();
 *
 * const collector = new TurnDiagnosticsCollector({ session, logger });
 * collector.attach(session);
 *
 * // … call proceeds …
 *
 * await session.close();
 * collector.detach();
 * ```
 *
 * ## Custom callback
 *
 * ```ts
